snippet.title: "ShootStar"released!
snippet.description:
SteamURL:https://store.steampowered.com/app/2949840/_/
"Shoot Star" released! (on steam)
The price will be about $4.99.
Please put it on your Steam wishlist.

－ A boss battle game in 2D shooting action, drawn in a cartoon style! Test your skills in a galaxy of delightful stars! － 
There will be a jumping action stage and a shooting action stage.
